        <https://w3id.org/italia/real-estate/controlled-vocabulary/StateProperty/TipoCategoriaPatrimonialeImmobile/23C3C> ,
        <https://w3id.org/italia/real-estate/controlled-vocabulary/StateProperty/TipoCategoriaPatrimonialeImmobile/23C3P> ,
